<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;CAHIER D’ANDILLY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONTRIBUTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cahier d’Andilly is a citizen contribution document from Andilly, detailing opinions and proposals regarding public services, taxation, and governance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cahier d’Andilly is a citizen contribution that expresses various grievances and proposals regarding fiscal, political, justice, immigration, and health issues."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Cahier d'Andilly serves as a formal document of grievances and demands from citizens of Andilly, contributing to the national consultation process."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-6298e8ced989441120884d3f8f99b6d2</data>
  <data key="d3">"CAHIER D’ANDILLY"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CSG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"REFORMEFISCALE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CSG (Contribution Sociale Généralisée) relates to the tax on retirement incomes and is a central concern for retirees."&lt;SEP&gt;"CSG is a tax that is deemed unjust for its uniform rates applied to all citizens, except for very low incomes."&lt;SEP&gt;"CSG refers to the General Social Contribution, which the citizen criticizes for its increase on pensions."&lt;SEP&gt;"CSG, or Contribution Sociale Généralisée, is mentioned in relation to the proposal of its removal for certain income brackets."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-ad5dafb597ab379106caef4e30f1bd96&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-4f321d3ee86dba0ea637c824e80ef331</data>
  <data key="d3">"CSG"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C2"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C2_C0"}, {"level": 2, "cluster": "L0C2_C0_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOI PINEL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Loi Pinel is criticized for benefiting the wealthy and is proposed for abolition."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"LOI PINEL"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMPÔT SUR LE REVENU&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Impôt sur le revenu (income tax) should account for taxes already paid, as noted in the context of grievances regarding double taxation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"IMPÔT SUR LE REVENU"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONTRIBUTION SOLIDAIRE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Contribution solidaire is seen as a burden on retirees, leading to an expressed need for its cessation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONTRIBUTION SOLIDAIRE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RETRAITES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Retraites (pensions) form a significant theme in the grievances, focusing on the calculation and taxation of retirement income."&lt;SEP&gt;"Retraites refer to pensions which should be indexed to the cost of living to ensure sustainability for retirees."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"RETRAITES"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PROPORTIONNELLE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A proposal for proportional representation in politics, which is linked to demands for democracy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Proportionnelle refers to a proposed electoral system using proportional representation to enhance political diversity."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROPORTIONNELLE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VOTE ÉLECTRONIQUE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vote électronique (electronic voting) is criticized as a potential means for electoral fraud."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"VOTE ÉLECTRONIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RENATIONALISER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Renationaliser refers to the proposal to renationalize services like EDF (Electricité de France), highways, and the postal service."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"RENATIONALISER"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PEINE CAPITALE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Peine capitale (death penalty) is proposed for those committing terrorist acts seen as acts of war against the Nation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"PEINE CAPITALE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMMIGRATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Immigration is a significant concern, with specific attitudes presented towards different categories of immigrants."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"IMMIGRATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;QUARANTAINE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Quarantaine refers to the proposed quarantine of immigrants from Africa due to health concerns, emphasizing the importance of border control."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"QUARANTAINE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FISCALITÉ&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fiscalité (taxation) is a broad theme discussed in the contribution, encompassing various aspects of tax policies and their impact on citizens."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fiscalité refers to issues related to taxation, specifically the proposal to review tax brackets due to significant disparities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fiscalité refers to the theme of taxation, central to the citizens' discussions about reforms and proposals regarding income and wealth."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-ad5dafb597ab379106caef4e30f1bd96&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-4f321d3ee86dba0ea637c824e80ef331</data>
  <data key="d3">"FISCALITÉ"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C3"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C3_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POLITIQUE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Politique (politics) reflects the contributors' opinions on governance, electoral systems, and representation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Politique involves the overarching themes related to governance, ideologies, and citizen engagement in political processes."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-62390ae432831ab71dd8fa0da68ff725</data>
  <data key="d3">"POLITIQUE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;JUSTICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Justice is a significant theme covering proposed changes to the legal system and its penalties for crimes."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"JUSTICE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMMIGRATION RÉFUGIÉS DE GUERRE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The acceptance of immigration for réfugiés de guerre (war refugees) is presented as a specific stance towards humanitarian issues."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"IMMIGRATION RÉFUGIÉS DE GUERRE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉFÉRENDUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The call for a Référendum (referendum) for major issues indicates a desire for direct democracy and citizen participation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉFÉRENDUM"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FICHÉS S&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fichés S refers to individuals with a particular security status in the context of proposed isolation measures."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"FICHÉS S"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PETITS DÉLINQUANTS ÉTRANGERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The call for the expulsion of petits délinquants étrangers (petty foreign offenders) highlights issues related to immigration and crime."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"PETITS DÉLINQUANTS ÉTRANGERS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONTRIBUTIONS FISCALES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Contributions fiscales (tax contributions) are broadly critiqued, pointing towards transparency and fairness in taxation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONTRIBUTIONS FISCALES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ECONOMIE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Economie (economy) is an overarching theme, related to fiscal and other socio-political considerations."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"ECONOMIE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FRONTIÈRES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Frontières (borders) are referenced in discussions about health safety measures related to immigration."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"FRONTIÈRES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RACKET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Racket refers to the perceived exploitation of retirees through financial policies, highlighting grievances over taxation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"RACKET"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMPÔTS SUR IMPÔTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Impôts sur impôts (tax on taxes) is a criticism regarding the fairness of the tax system, seen as burdensome for citizens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"IMPÔTS SUR IMPÔTS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DIMINUTION CSG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Diminution CSG refers to the proposal for a reduction in the Contribution Sociale Généralisée, aimed at relieving retirees."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"DIMINUTION CSG"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INDEXATION DES RETRAITES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Indexation des retraites indicates a proposal for actual adjustment of pensions to inflation rates, addressing economic concerns."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"INDEXATION DES RETRAITES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POLITIQUE DE SANTÉ&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Politique de santé (health policy) encompasses the implications of health measures on citizens, particularly regarding immigration."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"POLITIQUE DE SANTÉ"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LUTTE CONTRE LE TERRORISME&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The call for stronger measures in the Lutte contre le terrorisme (fight against terrorism) signifies public safety concerns."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"LUTTE CONTRE LE TERRORISME"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRANSPARENCE FISCALE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Transparence fiscale (tax transparency) emphasizes a need for clarity and fairness in taxation policies."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"TRANSPARENCE FISCALE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONFIANCE ENVERS LES INSTITUTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"NIVEAUCONFIANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Confiance envers les institutions refers to citizens' trust in public institutions, often questioned in light of the proposed reforms."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONFIANCE ENVERS LES INSTITUTIONS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DÉMOCRATIE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"COURANTIDEOLOGIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Démocratie (democracy) reflects the ideological framework within which the contributors express their opinions on governance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Démocratie represents the overall goal of achieving a more participative and equitable democratic system as envisioned by the citizens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-6298e8ced989441120884d3f8f99b6d2</data>
  <data key="d3">"DÉMOCRATIE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C0_C0"}, {"level": 2, "cluster": "L0C0_C0_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SERVICES PUBLICS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"SERVICEPUBLIC"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Services Publics refers to essential public services such as education, police, army, hospitals, and courts that are vital for societal cohesion."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services publics (public services) play a crucial role in the discussion, with proposals focusing on their management and nationalization."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"SERVICES PUBLICS"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C1_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉCUPÉRATION DES SERVICES STRATÉGIQUES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Récupération des services stratégiques refers to the proposal for reclaiming control over critical public services to safeguard national interests."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉCUPÉRATION DES SERVICES STRATÉGIQUES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉFORMES FISCALES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"REFORMEFISCALE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Réformes fiscales (tax reforms) are urged in the contribution, aiming to create a fairer and more effective tax system."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉFORMES FISCALES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;OBLIGATION DE DÉCLARATION DES BIENS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Obligation de déclaration des biens emphasizes proposals for ensuring transparency in personal financial declarations."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBLIGATION DE DÉCLARATION DES BIENS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DÉMOGRAPHIE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Démographie (demography) encompasses the population aspects related to public policy discussions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Démographie concerns the population dynamics and demographics addressed in discussions related to social policy and resources."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-4f321d3ee86dba0ea637c824e80ef331</data>
  <data key="d3">"DÉMOGRAPHIE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COHÉSION SOCIALE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cohésion sociale refers to the perceived lack of social cohesion amidst growing economic disparities."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8</data>
  <data key="d3">"COHÉSION SOCIALE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENGAGEMENT CITOYEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Engagement Citoyen clusters concepts relating to citizen participation, political involvement, and civic responsibility."&lt;SEP&gt;"Engagement citoyen (citizen engagement) is highlighted as a crucial aspect of democratic participation and public discourse."&lt;SEP&gt;"Engagement citoyen refers to the active participation of citizens in civic matters, underscoring the importance of political engagement."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e9b0763d7a2c12c61f8ccfb8e35ef7d8&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-62390ae432831ab71dd8fa0da68ff725&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-4f321d3ee86dba0ea637c824e80ef331</data>
  <data key="d3">"ENGAGEMENT CITOYEN"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REVENDICATIONS ANDILLY MARANS COURÇON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONTRIBUTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A collective contribution from Andilly, outlining various demands and proposals concerning governance, taxes, and social justice issues."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6298e8ced989441120884d3f8f99b6d2</data>
  <data key="d3">"REVENDICATIONS ANDILLY MARANS COURÇON"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C0_C0"}, {"level": 2, "cluster": "L0C0_C0_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RIC CARL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The RIC CARL (Référendum d'Initiative Citoyenne) is a proposed referendum mechanism allowing citizens to initiate legislation, amend laws, and recall elected officials."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6298e8ced989441120884d3f8f99b6d2</data>
  <data key="d3">"RIC CARL"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C0_C0"}, {"level": 2, "cluster": "L0C0_C0_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ISF&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"REFORMEFISCALE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"ISF (Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune) is a tax that concerns wealth distribution in France, proposed to be reinstated by citizens."&lt;SEP&gt;"ISF, or Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune, is a tax that citizens propose reinstating, indicating a concern for wealth taxation."&lt;SEP&gt;"ISF, or Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune, was a wealth tax suggested to be reinstated to balance the decrease in CSG."&lt;SEP&gt;"The ISF (Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune) refers to a proposed reintroduction of a wealth tax aimed at addressing economic inequalities."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-62390ae432831ab71dd8fa0da68ff725&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-6298e8ced989441120884d3f8f99b6d2&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-4f321d3ee86dba0ea637c824e80ef331</data>
  <data key="d3">"ISF"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C8"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TVA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"REFORMEFISCALE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"VAT (Taxe sur la Valeur Ajoutée) is mentioned in context of proposing reductions for essential goods and increases for luxury items."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-6298e8ced989441120884d3f8f99b6d2</data>
  <data key="d3">"TVA"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}, {"level": 1, "cluster": "L0C0_C0"}, {"level": 2, "cluster": "L0C0_C0_C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BANQUE DE FRANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
