<node id="&quot;ANDILLY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TERRITOIRE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Andilly is a French commune referenced in the contribution as the location of the citizen expressing grievances and proposals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Andilly is a commune in France where the citizen resides and is participating in the Grand Débat National."&lt;SEP&gt;"Andilly is a specific commune in France represented in the Grand Débat through its citizens' contributions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Andilly is a specific commune noted in the citizen consultation as the location related to the grievances and proposals made by citizens."</data>
