<node id="&quot;TRANSITION ÉCOLOGIQUE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal emphasizes the need for an ecological transition without imposing additional taxes, allowing people time to adapt their vehicles or heating systems according to their financial means."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transition Écologique refers to the ecological shift aimed at sustainability and the adoption of renewable energies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transition Écologique refers to the theme of transitioning to eco-friendlier practices for public services and companies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transition écologique encompasses the environmental changes needed to promote sustainability and is tied to the citizen's proposals."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-ad5dafb597ab379106caef4e30f1bd96&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-6e0daf98a008826c1777e642f6701058&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-39ade0b3466f1c17b3b29d9ce86a2bee&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-21ae39a2ff3f01a9b8dce8e2b91c0fcd</data>
  <data key="d3">"TRANSITION ÉCOLOGIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C6"}]</data>
</node>
