</node>
<node id="&quot;TAXE SUR LES RETRAITES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal suggests the removal of a 1.2% tax imposed on pensions, reflecting the citizen's stance on fiscal policies affecting retirees."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-21ae39a2ff3f01a9b8dce8e2b91c0fcd</data>
  <data key="d3">"TAXE SUR LES RETRAITES"</data>
