</node>
<node id="&quot;TAXE D'HABITATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal advocates for the reinstatement of the housing tax, updated according to property values, to ensure municipalities receive adequate funding without raising property taxes."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-21ae39a2ff3f01a9b8dce8e2b91c0fcd</data>
