</node>
<node id="&quot;LIMITATION DE VITESSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal calls for a reassessment of the speed limit set at 80 km/h, suggesting it be adjusted based on the danger level of specific roads."</data>
